-- China's Finance Ministry to Sell 23.2 Billion Yuan Local Government Bonds
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-07T01:58:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/china-s-finance-ministry-to-sell-23-2-billion-yuan-local-government-bonds.html

          
          
             China Ministry of Finance plans to
sell 23.2 billion yuan ($3.4 billion) of three-year bonds for
seven local governments on July 17, according to a statement
posted to the Chinabond website today.  
